             is charged by</p>
               <p>"Mary Davis, for attempting a rape on</p>
               <p>"her body at twelve o'clock;" is that the charge you made? - Yes, that night.</p>
               <p>Now the next day? - At that time the women were present.</p>
               <p>Court. What was the charge?</p>
               <p>Mr. Garrow. I will read it? -</p>
               <p>"August</p>
               <p>"27th, 
